methods.comment:
* Smsback invoked when an outgoing sms is sent to an emergency number. *

* This method will be called when an emergency sms is sent on any subscription, * regardless of which subscription this callback was registered on. * * @param sentEmergencyNumber The {@link EmergencyNumber} the emergency sms was sent to. * @param subscriptionId The subscription ID used to send the emergency sms.

methodNames: void onOutgoingEmergencySms(@NonNull EmergencyNumber sentEmergencyNumber, int subscriptionId)
